#: art_admin_slemicro.xml:1071
#, no-c-format
msgid "Users administration only for server administrators"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: art_admin_slemicro.xml:1072
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only users with the <guimenu>Server administrator</guimenu> role can edit "
"other users."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: art_admin_slemicro.xml:1077
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cockpit enables you to manage users of your system. Click <guimenu>Accounts</"
"guimenu> to open the user administration page. Here you can create a new "
"account by clicking <guimenu>Create new account</guimenu> or manage already "
